<!--pages/tutor/tutor-main/tutor-main.wxml-->
<view class="scroll-view">
  <view class="logo-style">
    <image style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" mode="aspectFill" src="/assets/img/logo_tutor.svg"></image>
  </view>
  <view>
    <i-notice-bar icon="systemprompt" loop>
      2019年毕业生，毕业设计答辩将于下周(5月18日)开展，请各位同学抓紧时间，积极准备。加油，好孩子！
    </i-notice-bar>
  </view>

  <i-grid>
    <navigator url='../../pages/double-allocation/double-allocation'>
      <i-grid-item>
        <i-grid-icon>
          <i-icon type="group" size="28" color="#80848f" />
        </i-grid-icon>
        <i-grid-label>双选分配</i-grid-label>
      </i-grid-item>
    </navigator>

    <navigator url='../../pages/weekly/weekly'>
      <i-grid-item>
        <i-grid-icon>
          <i-icon type="task" size="28" color="#80848f" />
        </i-grid-icon>
        <i-grid-label>周报</i-grid-label>
      </i-grid-item>
    </navigator>

    <navigator url='../../pages/graduation/graduation'>
      <i-grid-item>
        <i-grid-icon>
          <i-icon type="brush" size="28" color="#80848f" />
        </i-grid-icon>
        <i-grid-label>校外毕设</i-grid-label>
      </i-grid-item>
    </navigator>
  </i-grid>


  <i-grid>
    <navigator url='../../pages/materials/materials'>
      <i-grid-item>
        <i-grid-icon>
          <i-icon type="brush" size="28" color="#80848f" />
        </i-grid-icon>
        <i-grid-label>实习材料</i-grid-label>
      </i-grid-item>
    </navigator>
    <navigator url='../../pages/interim-report/interim-report'>
      <i-grid-item>
        <i-grid-icon>
          <i-icon type="brush" size="28" color="#80848f" />
        </i-grid-icon>
        <i-grid-label>期中汇报</i-grid-label>
      </i-grid-item>
    </navigator>
  </i-grid>
